Package: statswift
Title: Fast and Friendly Descriptive Statistics and Data Summaries
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Allen", "Zagic", email = "allen032@icloud.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: statswift provides a clean, intuitive toolkit for performing
    descriptive statistics and data summaries in R. It offers functions for
    computing extended summary statistics, detecting outliers, summarizing
    distributions, comparing groups, and generating formatted data reports.
    The package uses both S3 and S4 class systems to demonstrate object-oriented
    design in R. Designed for students, analysts, and researchers who want
    fast, readable statistical summaries without heavy dependencies.
